{"word":"ἐπιζητέω","slug":"ἐπιζητέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπιζητέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ζητέω\">ζητέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘try to find’ <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>, <b>look for, search for <a href='B:470 6:32'>Mt 6:32</a>; <a href='B:490 4:42'>Lk 4:42</a>; <a href='B:510 12:19'>Ac 12:19</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘show strong interest in’, <b>seek, want <a href='B:470 12:39'>Mt 12:39</a>; <a href='B:490 12:30'>Lk 12:30</a>; <a href='B:510 13:7'>Ac 13:7</a>; <a href='B:510 19:39'>19:39</a></b> (<el>ἐ.</el> = wish to know); <b><a href='B:520 11:7'>Ro 11:7</a>; <a href='B:570 4:17'>Phil 4:17</a>; <a href='B:650 11:14'>Hb 11:14</a>; <a href='B:650 13:14'>13:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιεικία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιθανάτιος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}